Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那么庞大的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非得要我一个人来扫除呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点扫除完  到行人大人那里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:30.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（别给我擅自把它吃掉  姐）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别给我擅自把它吃掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经吃掉了——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:15.00,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑吧  摆脱吧  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龙神社…真的是在足够高的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我把这些萝卜给千鹤小姐送去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人就先在这里休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里没事了  快下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你是特意来见我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是我的妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么妹妹的…话说  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但那孩子不在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直在找
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  麻知姐是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧  行人不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐是绫音的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  作为姐姐的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么是妻子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鹤小姐不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈的话在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概在厨房关着门而没有听到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在做红豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红豆大福？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鹤小姐做的红豆大福  非常好吃的哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如此  富有弹性的皮  味道浓郁的馅…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  口水流下来了…口水…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  去把绫音找来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:03:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音她又做什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了的话就给你妈妈特制的这软呼呼的红豆大福二十个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红豆大福  二十个？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯  无论如何我都会去找的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  铃拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接受寻找绫音这种事  没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可认为没那么容易就找出来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音的胸部是洗衣板～！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洗衣板…洗衣板…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁～是洗衣板啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  从对面马上就跑过来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:05:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在发育中  绝对不是洗衣板的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音啾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  不知道  不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,召唤作战大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音  现在是不会下手的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点钻进这麻袋里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐唆使的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  抓住绫音的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以得到二十个红豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可和麻知姐约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  真没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你这不是犯罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:31.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么感觉和平时相反了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.67,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情也不打招呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:34.94,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,锵～红豆大福！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,纹次郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红豆大福逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么连我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃那家伙还真拼命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那家伙一旦关系到甜品的话就性情大变了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是  我家妈妈做的秘传红豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是铃最爱中的最爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被红豆大福所收买的铃简直就是解开锁链的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但坦诚的向麻知道歉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,道歉也没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人不知道姐姐大人真正的可怕之处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,单单是回忆就很恐惧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要成为姐姐的实验体要有这样差点被杀死的遭遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  姐姐大人  不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音  别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能让绫音怕成这样  麻知究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红豆大福找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  来我这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红豆大福…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来做个交易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能找出我姐姐的弱点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你比姐姐多十个  也就是三十个红豆大福  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个怎么说都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三十个？接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么简单就被收买了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐的弱点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么麻知姐本人最清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去问问看～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情不可能会告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但铃去问的话  会有意外的收获哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我们这边也去打听姐姐的弱点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正结果都能预料了  放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果  什么结果？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐头的弱点？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外人也许会比家里人更加容易注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐头的弱点吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:08:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  确实以前说过  讨厌南边田野里的大牛蛙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等着吧  大牛蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  记得大牛蛙会有把靠近周围的人都吞噬的属性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心点的话 会很危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你解释的也太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知小姐所讨厌的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能回想起什么姐姐的弱点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也没期待你这小鬼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别叫我小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是弱点不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她以前捉弄我  看我不会吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就感觉到无聊  那种小事倒是有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐总是拿别人的反映作为取乐的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说无论怎么捉弄  只要我没反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会继续下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:08:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵呵呵  姐姐  既不痛也不痒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～  不管是谁也好  快来阻止她！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  如果我没反应的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐一定会更加凶暴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是没找到姐姐的一击致命的弱点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  还是在下手之前就此作罢怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了  绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐的弱点知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  伟大  我没期待错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「心脏被刀或矢所刺到就会死」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  那就是说你的心脏被什么刺到就不会死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是  太不甘心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有其它的什么吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就没有能让那过气的老婆婆一击致命的弱点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过气？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  姐姐已经18岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是个过气过了妙龄的老女人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（过气）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.62,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（老女人）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  这样说的话  麻知姐她会失落的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然背叛我了  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把姐姐大人带过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为快点让你们见面和好才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  原来是这样想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  如果带她来绫音这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐说她就给我50个红豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是红豆大福吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打击…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了  麻知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看姐姐这失落的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说姐姐很在意自己的年龄问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,惊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈  终于找到姐姐的弱点了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老相  老婆婆  过气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这一时刻  我才把稻草人一直藏着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  你就什么都做不了哦  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老相  老相～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,式神召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老相  老相～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还有那种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人  饶恕我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不～要～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前面的路会变窄了  小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  铃才要小心脚下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经习惯这路…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:11:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:06.59,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,吃惊吧  恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摔到屁股了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是因为昨天下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路变得容易滑倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  要人小心点的本人却自己掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  居然取笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉  真没受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  只是擦到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  感觉有什么撞到屁股了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀  地藏菩萨被撞坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么会在这么偏僻的角落里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把地藏菩萨撞坏了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会被诅咒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  就这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地藏菩萨可不是普通的地藏菩萨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一百年前有个干尽坏事的恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是当时巫女封印在这里  并且制成了石像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  并不是完全没事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样  这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我屁股肿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要特意让我看了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我自己又看不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊  行人一点都不害怕幽灵或妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事都是因为害怕  所以才会把虚无的东西看成幽灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再说我对那些鬼怪之类的不科学的东西没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只相信自己所见的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  铃把那地藏菩萨给…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  凛你们也知道啊  那个传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是岛上七大不可思议之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这样看上去铃就像是妖怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚开始就一直这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,半夜吵闹不听  差点被她掐死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全睡眠不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话  来我家留宿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  我家的被子可是很软的  公子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家有西洋的床哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是双人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看着如此害怕的铃  不做些什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  如果真的被恶灵附身的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  连千影和凛都相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…因为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从小时候就听说过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊  所谓传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了不让小孩接近危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才编造出来的大人的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说  骗小孩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说我「小孩」～！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在说梦话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么鬼魂  妖怪  诅咒什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  铃也别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在铃背后有白色的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:06.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  行人  振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:15:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有这么捉弄铃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  铃被附身也是事实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凭着这继承巫女之血的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到附在铃背后恶灵的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被附身的话  无论何时何地都会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最后把铃的灵魂拖入冥府为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  不要说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了不要这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  绫音那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是越来越严重了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点出来吧  吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说起来  真意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃也有害怕的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了今晚能心情舒适的睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再吓一吓铃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么这样害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本从小开始就比别人更害怕幽灵之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上一个人不敢在黑暗的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人生活后  稍微能适应了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但一旦听到可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕的话就会觉得很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每当我害怕的时候  一直都是妈妈安慰着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  一旦害怕  就会回忆起妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕和悲伤交织在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  不是还有我在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也许不能像铃的妈妈那样温柔的安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但在当铃感到害怕  寂寞的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会在你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得同情你  想老实的回去的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是两个人的气氛不错  感觉真讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是稍微吓她一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  面具放在哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出…出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是来吓唬铃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚…刚才  在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有恶灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人  我…好害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被附身了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…恶灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  那种东西像平常那样扔飞不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这时候  才是受过除灵训练的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天才美少女巫女绫音的出场！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了  行人一个人也好快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样说也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别舔我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑也是要有程度的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  不害怕吗  那是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这世界上像幽灵妖怪这样不科学的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是绝对不存在的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:41.67,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（存在被完全否定）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为大家认定它是恶灵妖怪什么的才害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它才会放肆恶作剧的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是什么恶灵  我会和大家说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以再恶作剧了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好  你也很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也算是除灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,消…消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙走的好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说那家伙根本没有脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是妖怪会是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会是白熊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很累了  回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  有行人在  就算做恶梦也不会害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请不要再掐我脖子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:10.04,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,「寻找熊熊」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是害怕啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把我放回原样吧…
